      "content": "i mean i've heard about serotonin syndrome but it sounds like something that only happens if you take way too much, right? i was just thinking of taking a standard dose of the supplement to see if it helps with the finals stress. it's just a herbal thing, so it shouldn't be as intense as the prescription med. do you think it's really that big of a deal if i just take a little bit?",
